Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是之前在日向家裏露營時發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從富士山那裏看肯定更漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.26,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(530,416)}去看看富士山吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是楓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 謝謝你們今天能來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這幾個人還稱不上各位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想商量什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵對富士山有興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想給小葵一個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假裝是在爬沒什麼特色的山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間 讓她看到富士山 大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楓 你知道什麼好地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用指南書來找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地域 難易度 做了很多分類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了小葵我可要加油呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離富士山近的是丹澤 南阿爾卑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張照片真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北嶽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多花田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 花田 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鳥 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼美妙 北嶽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 你找到好地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北嶽 真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}北嶽標準高度3143米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本第二高峰 比富士山更難 面向高手的山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去還不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少選個面向中級者的山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有其他合適的山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看見富士山的山對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 每個都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多的山太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的山僅僅是在富士山附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹澤山系 秩父山地 八岳 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍著它的山多著去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真難選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就選打開的下一頁上面的山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太隨便了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候就要一鼓作氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡山 標準高度1786米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在富士山附近 登山途中南側可以眺望富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西側可以眺望南阿爾卑斯山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山頂的正下面有一個叫做「屏風巖」的絕壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是著名的攀巖聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既可以看見富士山 又沒有那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼給小葵驚喜的山就決定是三增卡山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那天之前青不要告訴小葵要去哪裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次爬三增卡 很是期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去告訴小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 從飯能也能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向打過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 從飯能能看到富士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次爬的山已經決定下來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真突然 是哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點先保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週六早上六點在東飯能車站集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是飯能 是東飯能哦 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周…她打算帶我去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我還有點小期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾 換洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是什麼樣的山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李這些就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從三增卡站 順著登山道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我們能清楚的看到富士山 願明天天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去八王子 在那裏換乘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說要去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再去大月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說要保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裏走要30分鐘左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微睡一會也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是睡著更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}葭池溫泉前 下吉田 月江寺 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明白白地說了富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還能清清楚楚的看到富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡山呢 從終點河口湖下車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在卡嚓卡嚓山坐纜車登山雖然很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是從一開始就能看見富士山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以雖然有點累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要從三增卡站那裏爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得越是累 看到富士山的時候感動就越大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說從路上的屏風巖看富士山非常美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏給葵一個大驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡站？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裏到登山道要30分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼必要瞞著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}覺得好可怕 好可怕啊 往後一看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 good job
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前途多舛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像從剛才開始一直都是很普通的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太像是山路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一進山路馬上就是山頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為山頂是那個吧 那個像觸角一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說是三增卡登山道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫了南無阿彌陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在祈願登山平安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山…讀什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山祗神社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願我們能夠平安歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是公共廁所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瀑布呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫做神鈴瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日語中神鈴和心靈讀法一樣 心靈有靈魂之意 泛指由靈魂引起的超常現象
